text:
You ever hear that if you raise a
flower you planted yourself,
your wish'll come true when it
blooms? I kinda don't believe that,
but try it out on these and lemme
know what happens!

I went off to a class reunion, and
can you believe what I won in a
raffle? I'm never gonna need this
thing, but you might. If you don't,
feel free to sell it or give it away
or whatever. Up to you.

I saw these clothes for sale and
couldn't pass them up. I used to
wear this kinda thing all the time
back in my wild days (and low-key
still do sometimes) and I bet it'd
look rockin' on you.

You making sure to take some time
off to catch your breath? I talk a
lot about pushing yourself, but do
that too much and you'll burn out.
So lie down, put on some tunes,
and let the stress melt away!

Would you believe I found some
furniture I don't use anymore just
lying around? How do you LOSE a
whole piece of furniture? Life, I'm
telling you. Just be careful with it.
I don't know where it's been.
